Text: I pray Lord Hien is safe...
Pretenders! I will not suffer this mockery of ninjutsu!
What? Are they shinobi!?
Naught but pretenders! Our techniques are beyond their ilk!
They deploy machina even inside the castle!
That such a barbaric weapon should defile our beautiful castle...
It will not do so for much longer!
This aura... 'Tis as if he were a beast.
This aura... 'Tis as if he were a beast.
And one with nothing to lose.
All right, let's raise hells!
Aye! The more enemies we can draw, the better!
They're weapon transport containers.
Best destroy them here and now!
This appears to be a testing facility.
Well then, let's put this thing through its paces!
I'm afraid that's a fail.
A notable mention for its acceleration, however.
Something in those pods...
It couldn't be...people?
That they should so enhance men...
We must shut the pods down!
A third eye... That man is Garlean!
And he's undergone extensive enhancements.
A Garlean who can use magic...
It seems they seek to augment their people's weakness.
Another facility up ahead.
By the way it's set apart, I'd wager it's important.
They certainly do not want us here.
And that only makes it more inviting!
What is that thing? A machina or a beast?
Whatever it is, it's dangerous! Have care!
To the Royal Palace!
We strike hard and fast like a raging bull!
Sounds good to me! To the Royal Palace!
They've got some firepower, the Maelstrom!
Commander Rhiki has cleared the way for us!
Much obliged for the help!
The front gate's well defended as you'd expect.
A new type of weapon!?
A new type of weapon!?
New or old, Tizona will carve a path through it.
The way to the palace is clear!
No problems so far. I hope it's the same for the others.
No problems so far. I hope it's the same for the others.
We can but have faith and do our part. Come, the palace awaits!
Look! The others have made it in as well!
This is the moment of truth. Don't get complacent!
Well, I'll be! We might even have the upper hand!
This is the moment of truth. Don't get complacent!
Keep moving or you'll be an easy target!
Watch out! Artillery!
Move it, move it!
What in the world is that floating chair?
What's a scientist doing here...?
What's a scientist doing here...?
I mislike the look of this... Have care!
Wh-What just happened...?
To so gaze down on myself... A chilling experience...
To so gaze down on myself... A chilling experience...
Never imagined I'd miss my body so much...
As if a little barrier like this can stop us!
We're breaking through! Onward!
A few spells from a distance won't stop us!
We're breaking through! Onward!
Stiff defense they've got here...
The throne room is just ahead. And inside...
Stiff defense they've got here...
Not surprising─the throne room is just ahead.
Zenos! This time we settle this!
We have you at last, Zenos!
This time we settle this!
Quaaawk!
\<smack> \<slurp>
\<slurp> \<slurp>
Pfff-hssssss!
\<clank> \<whirr>
Ook-ook!
Three, two, one...kaboom!
Hyaaah!
Woof, woof!
Shine brilliant for me!
You can't escape the storm!
\<squint> \<squint>
Arruff.♪
If it were up to me...
I'd take this path!
They're on fire!
I don't think my fishing hook will be of use here!
I'd rather not do that again...
Get too close and you'll be in for a shock!
Do you think some monsters prefer rainy days over sunny days?
Those claws will cut us in two!
A crab that big could feed a whole village...
I was a bit worried there...but that's behind us now.
More ill-tempered beasts!
We're alive... We're still alive.
It's always worse when they fly...
Go away! Go away!
I said GO AWAY!
Gaaah!
You just going to stand there!? Cold-blooded bastards!
Maybe he shouldn't have set that beast upon us...
There's danger around every bend!
I'll be seeing you!
Not even a word of thanks.
They don't look very friendly!
Fish are close, I know it!
To the patient go the fish!
Oh, what's this? Such a strong bite!
To the patient go the fish!
Oh, what's this? Such a strong bite!
Sorry for wasting your time...
More of them...
Yes! I've hooked something!
It's weak, but a bite is a bite!
Oh my! This one's quite strong!
Someone's a fighter! But I won't let you get away!
Those things sent a chill down my spine.
A toad that big could swallow us whole!
I'm glad we didn't end up as its dinner...
Is that...a plant!? It's enormous!
I was afraid you'd be eaten alive!
Ugh... The hairs on my skin are standing on end.
Are those...caterpillars!?
Those rocks...they're moving!
What other surprises does this island have in store?
What a majestic bird...but that beak looks sharp as a sword!
The branches grew!
I've never seen a bat so large!
The bats in Thavnair are not nearly as big...or ferocious.
What are these?
Uwah! How did you─ Leave me alone!
Finally, statues that stay where they are.
May thoughts of Nidhana give me courage!
Ow! I stubbed my toe!
Oh! I got a bite!
Huzzah! A catch worth celebrating!
How annoying...
May thoughts of Nidhana give me courage!
\<heavy breathing> I think that shaved a few summers off my life.
Oh ho! I've hooked something big!
It's large, and it's heavy!
Hamsa! They really are everywhere.
I've had my fill of wild animals already...
The tree moves!
I didn't know coconuts could grow to such sizes.
Look, an asvattha! Just as horrifying here as they are in Thavnair.
No, even more horrifying...the asvattha here smell much worse.
Let's see. Any fishing spots to be found?
It's a dead end.
Who's that!? Or...what's that?
My legs don't want to move forward, but I must.
We've walked into a lizard den!
We can go further in from here.
I knew it─a trick!
Why did she get so angry? Was it something I said?
This is no way to treat visitors!
Crocs! Keep your distance!
Where did that faerie fly off to?
Look at the size of that thing!
There has to be a path somewhere...
<split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>, boars! A lot of them!
How deep does this path go?
Treasure chests? In a place like this?
Something's not right...
We can't go any further. We'll have to find another way.
They're alive!
That was too close for comfort... Grab the treasure so we can get out of here.
Th-These aren't treasure chests! What do we do!?
This doesn't look good... I'll leave it to you, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>!
This doesn't look good... I'll leave it to you, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>!
The mist is so thick I can barely see my own trunk...
The mist is so thick I can barely see my own trunk...
We are going forward, right?
A bite, and a strong one at that! I wonder what it is...
Hmm... That's quite the pull.
Oh!? This might be the big one!
They want the bait, but not enough to bite down hard...
Oh, this is it! Sisters give me strength!
I'll leave the fighting to you.
Well struck!
All right. Let's keep moving.
Let's go!
Someone help!
Aaahhh!
What has happened to this island?
They leave us no choice...
Are you all right?
Yes, thanks to you.
There. It should be safe to cross now.
Hold still!
No running off!
Careful!
Yaaaaaargh!
That was too close...
Steady now.
Dammit!
You'll pay for that!
Thank you.
Look out!
Try this!
Nothing to it.
Throw everything you have at it!
Impressive.
What have we here?
What manner of beast could it be?
How large do you suppose it is?
Even so, we should speak with the researchers first.
Such marks would be too common in any case.
The beast has feathers, eh?
So many strange plants you have here.
Ugh, that smell...
You said the beast is close?
Struck down defending its territory, most like.
We mustn't let any more creatures come to harm.
I see no tracks that match those claw marks...
What's this?
There has to be a clue here somewhere...
Focus. We've no time for picking flowers.
A Roegadyn? I thought this island was deserted?
Uwah! Stay away from me!
I need...I need a moment to catch my breath.
For Nidhana!
Hmm... Nothing wants to bite.
A rare catch awaits. I can feel it!
What is he up to!?
Ugh!
Damn, he's fast...
Hngh!
My turn!
Bleed!
Come on!
Hyah!
Fall already!
Hah!
Saw that coming.
Now!
Not this time!
\<squeak>
Squeeeaaak!
Wreeeeee!
Let's get started!
Hope you brought an umbrella!
Have you ever beheld such grace as mine!?
Phew...I'm going through a lot of bullets.
Oh no! My finger slipped!
Here. We. GO!
Run, run, run!
Hahaha!
You'll never guess what I've got in store...
Hehehe! Who made that sound? Rude!
Just step on a cushion! Pretty please?
Time to reload!
This scenery reminds me of home...
Gaaah! I'm not afraid, I'm not afraid...
Remember... Hardships make us strong!
This looks like a great spot to cast my rod.
Hmm... Not a single fish I haven't seen before.
I'll have a look!
Too bad!
Heh, lucky you.
What was in the chests, I wonder?
See how an expert fisher does it!
It's beautiful...
Good to see you found a way in too, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>.
Right, then! Let's go and get our treasure!
Up for some spearfishing, J'moldva?
Always.
What is that? Some kind of horse?
It's the Kelpie! I've heard legends of it!
I'm drenched from head to toe...
No more than you'd expect on an adventure, eh?
And I have a feeling it's crawling with “worshipers”...
I daresay this was a place of worship.
Quite well guarded, that door.
Does that mean we've already reached the treasure!?
If that's the treasure, then consider me disappointed.
Fortunately for you, it's another guardian. Be on your guard!
Hmph, troublesome piece of clay...
Indeed. Its magicks were not to be underestimated.
Prison cells...
Relics of the mad king's reign.
That was a person? Seven hells...
So the dark rumors of this place were true...
It seems that fellow won't let us have the treasure without a fight.
Wouldn't be much of an adventure if it didn't end on a climax, eh?
I...can't move...
From here we must proceed on foot.
That was quite a sandstorm...
All present and accounted for?
I believe so. Let us continue on foot.
Watch your heads, everyone!
The sand above gives way. Have care.
Falling rocks!
We've fallen quite a ways...
A scorpion clad in crystal. How curious.
I daresay we're in that creature's home.
What did it have to feed upon here?
Amazing that life could adapt to such a harsh environment.
One cannot underestimate the will to survive.
Is this Allagan...?
Quite an abrupt change in surrounds...
Aye. The aether here is unmistakable.
Ugh, repulsive creatures...
It seems we've trespassed upon their lair.
Never a dull moment in this cavern!
Native fauna or Allagan machina, we'll clear them all out!
Such an immense facility...
Both machina and facility are still operational.
Not for much longer, they won't be!
Those blades could do some serious damage.
Nothing to it.
As much as I would like to examine this place, we should press on.
Indeed. Perhaps there will be time later.
'Tis easy to see why they say this place was “bled dry.”
No matter the odds, life always finds a way...
The sand here is as pale as those enormous bones.
I'm glad we don't have to face it alive.
Are sandworms descended from this creature, I wonder.
That a sandworm could have grown to such proportions...
A dragon as white as these wastes... How very fitting.
That dragon formed from the mist!
Another of Allag's pitiable slaves, I'd wager.
This is the moment of truth, my friends! Hold nothing back!
Aye, let's give them hells!
They must do better than that to catch us off guard!
Out of our way!
Enemies from above!
Golden armor... Safe to assume it's dangerous.
Special, are you? Well, you're about to lose your luster!
Indeed. Let all have care.
Ungh, my head is spinning...
That was some truly savage swordplay.
Too close for comfort...
How fierce must the fighting have been here...
Machina wreckage!?
Our friends need us! With me!
Hang in there, Lyse!
My lord!
An unusual foe...but we will find a way through it!
Whatever it is, we can't afford to be stopped here!
Some manner of trench-digging weapon?
Such bizarre machina the Garleans are wont to make...
That one was like a fire-breathing mole, I thought.
Elder Seedseer! Ser Aymeric!
Let us press on together!
How heartening to have the Alliance's finest at our side!
You're all safe, thank goodness!
Aye, there is naught we need fear!
To ward off such a powerful attack...
No less than I'd expect of the Elder Seedseer!
A sturdier barrier I have seldom seen!
Leave it to Lyse to pierce warmachina armor with her fist!
I won't be outdone!
These are no ordinary soldiers...
So, their commanders deign to appear at last!
Make way for Zozone!
Ride the wind!
Serve up a storm!
Time to make myself scarce!
Heartless bastards! I'll have my revenge!
Shame I won't get to watch you die here!
It's gone berserk!
Does every beast on this island want to kill us?
I admit...that was scary, but exciting.
Have at you!
Enough!
Fear my wrath!
I think not.
With me, Golbez!
Are you all right?
For king and country!
I cannot─will not─fall here!
It's Lord Golbez!
Lord Golbez is come!
And Lord Durante too!
Thank heavens you've returned!
Arrrggghhh!
Help...me...
Lord Golbez! Lord Durante!
Quickly, to the castle!
They've returned! Thank heavens!
Lord Golbez! Hope is not lost, then!
Please, no!
What's happening to me!?
Run for your lives!
Ahhh!
Someone help us!
Peep-peep!
\<rumble> \<rumble>
Wind guide my arrow!
Work hard, play harder!

I shall deliver the
world its salvation!
Ruff!
Woo-hoo-hoo!
Peg, peg!
Hyaaah!
Darkness...
Are you prepared?
You don't need a reason.
\<slurp>
One!
Two!
Three!
Four!
Five!
Six!
We will deal with this fiend!
Forward! Forward!
For Baron!
Leave this one to us!
Allow me to assist you!
Let us press onward!
We must hurry to the castle!
The city is in ruins...
Onward!
I shudder to think what other horrors yet await us.
I leave the rest to you.
Hurry, Golbez!
What in the seven hells!?
Wh-What's happened to my body?
Ye gods, what magick is this!?
Grrr, just you wait!
A truly vexing spell...
Ugh, not again!
Don't take your eyes off them!
This can't be good... Stay on guard!
You'll not find me an easy target!
So they mean to play their trump card!
Throw everything you've got at them!
We must finish this before they can!
What's gotten into this thing!?
Try aiming for its wings!
One step at a time...
Oh, you ruined it! I'd packed the chests full of goodies, too!
You aren't going to jump...are you?
I can do this! I can!
Every twist and turn brings us face-to-face with a new threat...
Finally, a chance to fish!
Do you think she's telling the truth, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>?
Look at this, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>!
Huh!? What is this fish?
The slightest touch should be enough to clear it...
The wind made it brittle for us. Now we can pass through!
Let us reconvene at the castle garden.
Let's hope the divinities of Aloalo guide us true.
Nothing for it but to keep going!
We made it through the mist!
What!? It moved!
Didn't expect that. Well, no point in sticking around!
Yaaaaaahhh!
I almost fainted... Where are we?
Everywhere we go, beasts are waiting for us!
These caterpillars are blood-curdling...
It's quicker than it looks!
Hehe. Now this could be interesting.
I won't say no to treasure, but what I'm really here for is the fish!
Golbez's domain, at long last...
So there are voidsent after all. Have care.
This place is not at all as I remember it...
He's altered his domain, then?
I can sense its presence deep within... Zeromus is here.
Let's move on, before they have time to regroup.
Teleportation magick. Interesting...
Is this all Golbez can muster to bar our path?
I didn't expect such a beast to yet remain.
A formidable foe...
Even so, it pales before the archfiends.
The vanishing scepters were quite the nuisance.
That was easy enough.
As if cheap parlor tricks would suffice to stop us.
Vanished, you say? I thought they were merely bluffing.
A memoria crystal!?
This memoria crystal is... No, it can't be...
What's happening!?
Did that man just call you...Golbez?
I've met this man somewhere before...
This man seems to think you're Golbez.
'Twould seem we've become part of the memory.
Whoever this man is, he seems convinced you're Golbez.
They were too late to save their home, then...
So this is the kingdom of Baron.
Even if this is only a memory, it is no less easy to bear and watch.
If we're to escape, it seems we've no choice but to fight.
Are those fangs...or horns?
So this is an antlion of the Thirteenth.
